Package: helper-node
Version: 0.4.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Helper Node Team <support@helper-node.app>
Depends: libgtk-3-0t64 | libgtk-3-0, libnss3, libxss1, libxtst6, libasound2t64 | libasound2, libgbm1, libdrm2, xdg-utils, libatspi2.0-0t64 | libatspi2.0-0
Description: AI-powered voice assistant with Whisper transcription
 Helper Node is an Electron-based application that transcribes audio queries 
 using Whisper and displays AI-generated responses in a user-friendly interface.
 Features include syntax-highlighted code blocks, OCR from screenshots, and 
 global hotkeys for seamless OS integration.
 .
 Includes pre-compiled Whisper models for fast audio transcription.
